:0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"全球最大的公海賭場上線了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"講左咁多年，終於可以做返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>「施琅號」的前身為「瓦良格號」，是1980年代由蘇聯設計製造的航母，1992年「瓦良格號」還來不及完成，蘇聯就解體了，其所屬權於是轉至烏克蘭，90年代由澳門的中羅旅行社（音譯）花了兩千萬美元購買，中羅旅行社一般被外界認為隸屬於解放軍。<br />\n<br />\n該船還一度被土耳其政府阻擋在黑海之內，外傳土耳其政府因畏懼中共購買此航鑑的動機不單純，而中羅旅行社當時聲稱購買「瓦良格號」的理由是想將其打造成水上豪華賭場，才拖出黑海。後來，當然「瓦良格號」的最終目的地不是澳門，而是被拖航至大連港，並開始了解放軍打造「施琅號」的工程。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"36250d07a4b0c6f654b7dc8832775b64e7bc1eac","tid":2492263,"uid":383204,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6d9f4be32750821d7326368fc199db3b7a3c805","tid":2492263,"uid":173183,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17cb40e270609e463008644e416e02c1f42f2cb8","tid":2492263,"uid":125168,"like":82,"dislike":5,"score":77,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好意思啱啱瞓醒<br />\n哩壇野咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"解放軍跳老舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5fae1f1101794719df335188c6c19109bb3f0f","tid":2492263,"uid":345137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"如果係美軍電子攻擊就好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次中共向南海射導彈抗議, 2支跌左落支那境內, 2支落左南海, 但美軍仲快過中共回收個彈頭, 證明美軍一開始已經掌握曬導彈動向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46758fda7d843867e40c619096c7b7e72b0c5655","tid":2492263,"uid":2645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:18:19.000Z","msg":"做左賭船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi